his activity.<br/><br/><b>Excerpt</b>Experience Malaysia\'s slower pace of life on a day trip from Kuala Lumpur to the tribal region of Carey Island. You\'ll be introduced to the cultural traditions of the Mah Meri seafarers — a...<br/><br/><b>Inclusions</b>Lunch and snacks<br/>Local guide<br/>Hotel pickup and drop-off<br/><br/><b>Exclusions</b>Alcoholic drinks (available to purchase)<br/><br/><b>Additional Info</b>Confirmation will be received within 48 hours of booking, subject to availability<br/>Infant seats are available on request if advised at time of booking', null, '1.00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', '1', null, '1', '', '', null, '', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '', '', '2017-02-21 11:44:19', '6', null, '', 'default');
