by<br/><br/><b>Operations</b>Daily<br/><br/><b>Vourcher</b>You can present either a paper or an electronic voucher for this activity.<br/><br/><b>Excerpt</b>This full-day tour takes you outside of Kuala Lumpur city and gives you the opportunity to see what the surrounding areas have to offer. Start with a trip to the iconic Batu Caves, then make your...<br/><br/><b>Inclusions</b>Lunch<br/>Dinner<br/>Entrance fees<br/>Local guide<br/>Hotel pickup and drop-off<br/><br/><b>Exclusions</b>Personal expenses <br/><br/><b>Additional Info</b>Confirmation will be received within 48 hours of booking, subject to availability<br/>Dress code: formal<br/>A minimum of 2 people per booking is required', null, '1.00', '', '', '', '', '', '', '', null, null, '1', '', '', null, '', null, null, null, null, null, null, null, '', '', '2017-02-21 11:44:20', '6', null, '', 'default');
